# Local project files
# .afi-ops/ holds AFI-specific scripts, reports, and docs.
# It's already covered by the `.*` rule on line 3, listed here for visibility.
# .afi-ops/
#
# CLAUDE.md sits at the project root and is read by Claude for context.
# Keep it ignored so it doesn't end up in upstream PRs.
CLAUDE.md

# AGENTS.md mirrors CLAUDE.md (project context for other agentic tools)
# and contains live credentials. Must not be committed to a public repo.
AGENTS.md
